    "specialty": "Neurosurgery",
    "topic": "Comprhensive Surgery Revision conv.docx",
    "question": "What is the critical difference between frame-based and frameless stereotactic procedures?",
    "options": {
      "B": "The use of rendered three-dimensional images and a three-dimensional digitizer.",
      "D": "The presence of a lesion in the brain on digitized imaging studies.",
