      "B": "",
      "C": "",
      "D": "",
      "E": ""
    },
    "guideline": "Standard Surgical Board Review",
    "takeaway": "Key Insight: Loop diuretics, such as furosemide, are potent inhibitors of the sodium-potassium-chloride cotransporter. They act by co..."
