      "A": "",
      "B": "",
      "C": "",
      "D": "",
      "E": ""
    },
    "guideline": "Standard Surgical Board Review",
    "takeaway": "Key Insight: Bradykinins are vasodilators produced by kinino gen degradation by the protease kallikrein. Kallikrein circulates in blo..."
  },
