      "B": "",
      "C": "",
      "D": "",
      "E": ""
    },
    "guideline": "Standard Surgical Board Review",
    "takeaway": "Key Insight: Blood glucose levels are regulated by hormones in response to carbohydrate intake. Insulin secretion increases with inta..."
  },
