    "guideline": "WSES Jerusalem Guidelines on Acute Appendicitis",
    "takeaway": "Key Concept: Classic appendicitis in an adult male is a clinical diagnosis; definitive management is appendectomy (laparoscopic preferred).",
    "id": 795
  },
  {
