    },
    "guideline": "ASCRS Clinical Practice Guideline for the Treatment of Fecal Incontinence",
    "takeaway": "Key Concept: Obstetric sphincter injury + large defect (>90-120 deg) = Overlapping Sphincteroplasty.",
