      "E": "These are signs of pulmonary embolism or other lung pathology."
    },
    "guideline": "ATLS 10th Edition - Cardiac Tamponade",
    "takeaway": "Key Concept: Beck's Triad = Tamponade (Muffled heart sounds, JVD, Hypotension). Use FAST to confirm.",
