    },
    "guideline": "NCCN Guidelines - Pancreatic / HPB Malignancies",
    "takeaway": "Key Concept: Courvoisier's sign = Palpable non-tender GB + Painless jaundice \u2192 Periampullary malignancy (NOT stones).",
    "id": 843
},
